eserves for anticipated future expenses statements made in this press release are qualified by the cautionary statements made in this press release neither sandridge nor the trustee intends and neither assumes any obligation to update any of the statements included in this press release an investment in common units issued by sandridge permian trust is subject to the risks described in the trust’s annual report on form k for the year ended december   and all of its other filings with the sec the trust’s quarterly and other filed reports are or will be available over the internet at the sec’s web site at httpwwwsecgov contacts sandridge permian trustthe bank of new york mellon trust company na as trusteesarah newell  contacts sandridge permian trustthe bank of new york mellon trust company na as trusteesarah newell  search advanced news search advanced news search log in sign up careers – sandridge energy skip to content latest news sandridge energy inc announces  second quarter shareholder update and financial results release date and conference call information latest presentation menu  stock info no data yet a career with sandridgebecome part of the team a closer look at sandridge reveals what is most important to the company—our people beyond getting the job done working at sandridge is about being part of a team where people strive together toward common goals knowing their contribution matters to the company’s success starting from the top we’ve created a culture defined by hard work and an inner determination to never be satisfied with the status quo no matter the assignment our employees never stop looking for better safer and more cost effective ways to accomplish company goals we’re communityminded teamoriented and companyfocused proud to be the best in the industry student or upcoming college graduate this applies to any currently enrolled college students seeking internship opportunities and those upcoming college graduates looking for entrylevel employme